wikipedia_page.main: Stuart Carswell (born 9 September 1993) is a Scottish professional footballer, who plays as a midfielder for Scottish League One side Dumbarton. Carswell has previously played for Motherwell, St Mirren, as well as Icelandic side Keflavík.
